modShortDescription: Feel like the game is missing some blocks? This will be your mod. This 7 Days to Die mod adds a number of custom blocks to give the world a greater feel.
modDescription:
Feel like the game is missing some blocks? Then this will be your mod. This 7 Days to Die mod adds a number of custom blocks to give the world a greater feel. Guppycur will be adding to this quite a bit, so feel free to make suggestions.

[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Misc_Blocks)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/), Chiko
